**Additional Protections**:

- **Constant-time responses**: Prevents timing attacks that reveal document existence
- **Anomaly detection**: Automatic alerting when access patterns suggest enumeration attacks
- **Permission inheritance validation**: Users cannot grant permissions higher than their own (prevents privilege escalation)
- **Admin audit trail**: All admin overrides are logged and trigger security events for review
