Forced browsing on file resources is extremely common and dangerous. Attackers often discover predictable patterns like `/reports/2024/user_report_12345.pdf` and enumerate thousands of files. The 2023 First American Financial breach exposed 885 million records through similar direct object reference vulnerabilities in document URLs.

**PRODUCTION PATTERN**:

